arrow\u2010 and wide\u2010ranging species show distinct biogeographic patterns, and different taxonomic groups also unequally represent them.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Ruggiero, Adriana", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Kitzberger, Thomas", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/4c2e26cd009cced83d90f31f09609c24", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/ab8c633e5c2f4979f2df590c835309fe9b5f36a5ab6352f194ec60a747eb26bf", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/FLMYGQRY", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/FLMYGQRY", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/bfe4d2dd5a93c88faf2684cfd7f33173!/b294440-296934", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "4", "pages": "401-417", "title": "Ecography", "volume": "27"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/4c2e26cd009cced83d90f31f09609c24"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:FLMYGQRY"}, {"identifier": "10.1111/j.0906-7590.2004.03801.x"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosyslit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "13429499"}}]}}, "title": "Environmental correlates of mammal species richnes